[ Keyboard ticking ]

35:16.897 --> 35:19.029
[ Cellphone swoops ]

35:19.073 --> 35:22.859
♪♪

35:22.903 --> 35:26.515
[ Cellphone vibrates ]

35:26.559 --> 35:28.691
Yeah?

35:28.735 --> 35:30.171
Yeah.

35:30.215 --> 35:32.173
Yeah, what?

35:32.217 --> 35:34.175
Yeah,
we're doing it.

35:34.219 --> 35:37.483
I'll keep them in the cell, man,
for two weeks,

35:37.526 --> 35:39.746
and you'll get
those death certificates, man.

35:39.789 --> 35:43.010
You be the son, man.
Get that money, man.

35:43.053 --> 35:44.577
Then you give me
mine, man,

35:44.620 --> 35:47.536
for my special plan
with my special woman.

35:47.580 --> 35:50.191
[ Cellphone beeps ]

35:50.235 --> 35:57.329
♪♪

35:57.372 --> 36:04.553
♪♪

36:04.597 --> 36:07.817
[ Man speaking Spanish ]

36:07.861 --> 36:10.864
Brown --
Byron Brown.

36:10.907 --> 36:20.221
♪♪

36:20.265 --> 36:29.622
♪♪

36:29.665 --> 36:39.022
♪♪

36:39.066 --> 36:48.380
♪♪

36:48.423 --> 36:51.078
[ Indistinct conversations ]

37:14.928 --> 37:16.843
Mr. and Mrs. Brown?

37:16.886 --> 37:19.193
I'm Byron Brown.

37:19.237 --> 37:22.457
Our friend James --You know James?

37:22.501 --> 37:25.895
Our friend James told me
to expect you for your son.

37:25.939 --> 37:28.768
Please, would you
come with me?

37:28.811 --> 37:31.031
Out of the cold,
out of the line?

37:31.074 --> 37:33.686
I'll have you
taken care of quickly.

37:38.517 --> 37:41.737
Sorry, Mr. and Mrs. Brown,
but, as you can see,

37:41.781 --> 37:44.697
prison life here is different
than the U.S.

37:44.740 --> 37:47.961
Inmates greatly outnumber
the guards.

37:48.004 --> 37:51.312
I have to go to the hospital
unit to get your son.

37:51.356 --> 37:54.576
You can't go there,
so I'll bring him to you.

37:54.620 --> 37:59.320
For your safety, it's best
that I place you in here

37:59.364 --> 38:01.366
for your protection.

38:01.409 --> 38:04.847
It's a
minimum-security cell.

38:04.891 --> 38:07.894
These inmates offer
no threat.

38:07.937 --> 38:10.549
These are my sissies.

38:10.592 --> 38:13.987
Please step in.

38:14.030 --> 38:17.817
Or we can go out there,
back in that line.

38:17.860 --> 38:19.775
We can do that.

38:19.819 --> 38:23.083
Take four
or five hours.

38:23.126 --> 38:27.435
We put you in here for
expedition and safety purposes.

38:31.700 --> 38:43.103
I'll be just
a few minutes.

38:43.146 --> 38:49.239
♪♪

38:49.283 --> 38:55.333
♪♪

38:55.376 --> 38:57.944
[ Speaking Spanish ]

39:27.626 --> 39:31.151
I've just moved here, yes,
with my parents.

39:31.194 --> 39:32.674
They're getting older.

39:32.718 --> 39:35.024
I need to establish
a New Mexico license.

39:35.068 --> 39:37.026
Do you have
your birth certificate?

39:37.070 --> 39:39.246
Yeah.

39:39.289 --> 39:43.424
I have everything
I think I need.

39:43.468 --> 39:47.733
♪♪

